entry.value: select md5(nr) as h_item_hk, now() as load_date, 'erp.wctz.itemview' as record_source, -- conca md5(CONCAT_WS(',',nr,lft, rght, lvl, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, name, barcode, type, status, plan_strategy, lock_type, lock_expire_at, price_abc, qty_abc, cost, gross_weight, net_weight, physical_unit, project_nr, mpq, outer_package_num, pallet_num, outer_package_gross_weight, pallet_gross_weight, outer_package_volume, pallet_volume, plan_list_date, plan_delist_date, category, subcategory, description, owner_id)) as item_hash_diff, nr as item_nr, lft, rght, lvl, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, name, barcode, type, status, plan_strategy, lock_type, lock_expire_at, price_abc, qty_abc, cost, gross_weight, net_weight, physical_unit, project_nr, mpq, outer_package_num, pallet_num, outer_package_gross_weight, pallet_gross_weight, outer_package_volume, pallet_volume, plan_list_date, plan_delist_date, category, subcategory, description, owner_id from basic_item

select md5(nr) as h_location_hk, now() as load_date, 'erp.wctz.locationview' as record_source, md5(CONCAT_WS(',', nr, lft, rght, lvl, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, id, name, area, category, subcategory, description, available_id, owner_id))as location_hash_diff, nr as location_nr, nr, lft, rght, lvl, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, id, name, area, category, subcategory, description, available_id, owner_id from test_nifi.basic_location

select md5(CONCAT(item_id, location_id)) as l_inventory_hk, now() as load_date, item_id as item_nr, location_id as location_nr, md5(item_id) as h_item_hk, md5(location_id) as h_location_hk, 'erp.wctz.inventoryview' as record_source, md5(CONCAT_WS(',', item_id, location_id, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, type, onhand, available, category, subcategory, description)) as inventory_hash_diff, item_id, location_id, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, type, available, category, subcategory, description, SUM(onhand) as onhand from inventory_inventory group by l_inventory_hk, load_date, item_nr, location_nr, h_item_hk, h_location_hk, record_source, inventory_hash_diff, item_id, location_id, source, lastmodified, created_at, updated_at, type, available, category, subcategory, description

SELECT "item_id", "location_id", "type", "available", "category", "subcategory", "description", "created_at", "updated_at", SUM( "onhand" ) AS "onhand" FROM inventoryview GROUP BY "item_id", "location_id", "type", "available", "category", "subcategory", "description", "created_at", "updated_at"
